{
  "info": {
    "name": "ChurchManager API",
    "description": "Collection REST pour ChurchManager (Django REST Framework, multi-tenant SaaS).\n\n**Variables** : `base_url`, `token`, `refresh_token`.\n\nAprès **Login**, le script enregistre automatiquement `access` dans `token` et `refresh` dans `refresh_token`.\n\nLes routes métier exigent un JWT valide et une église (`church`) associée au compte (sauf SuperAdmin plateforme).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "church_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "fidele_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "cotisation_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "evenement_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "eglise_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "region_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (nouvelle église + admin)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"church_name\": \"Église Exemple\",\n  \"church_email\": \"contact@eglise-exemple.org\",\n  \"church_phone\": \"+22501020304\",\n  \"admin_email\": \"admin@eglise-exemple.org\",\n  \"admin_password\": \"Motdepasse123!\",\n  \"admin_first_name\": \"Jean\",\n  \"admin_last_name\": \"Dupont\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register/",
            "description": "**Réponse 201 (exemple)**\n```json\n{\n  \"church\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Église Exemple\", \"email\": \"...\", \"phone\": \"...\", \"created_at\": \"...\" },\n  \"user\": { \"id\": 1, \"email\": \"admin@...\", \"role\": \"admin_national\", \"church\": 1 },\n  \"detail\": \"Organisation créée. Vous pouvez vous connecter.\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "try {",
                  "  var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200 && json.access) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access);",
                  "    if (json.refresh) { pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh); }",
                  "    if (json.user && json.user.church) {",
                  "      pm.collectionVariables.set('church_id', String(json.user.church));",
                  "    }",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) { console.warn(e); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@eglise-exemple.org\",\n  \"password\": \"Motdepasse123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login/",
            "description": "**Réponse 200 (exemple)**\n```json\n{\n  \"refresh\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"access\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"email\": \"admin@...\",\n    \"first_name\": \"Jean\",\n    \"last_name\": \"Dupont\",\n    \"full_name\": \"Jean Dupont\",\n    \"role\": \"admin_national\",\n    \"church\": 1\n  }\n}\n```\n\nLe script de test enregistre `access` → variable `token` et `refresh` → `refresh_token`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "try {",
                  "  var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200 && json.access) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access);",
                  "    if (json.refresh) { pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh); }",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh/",
            "description": "**Réponse 200 (exemple)**\n```json\n{ \"access\": \"eyJ...\", \"refresh\": \"eyJ...\" }\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout/",
            "description": "**Réponse 200**\n```json\n{ \"detail\": \"Déconnexion réussie.\" }\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Profile (GET)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/profile/",
            "description": "**Réponse 200 (exemple)**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"email\": \"admin@...\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Jean\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Dupont\",\n  \"full_name\": \"Jean Dupont\",\n  \"phone\": \"\",\n  \"avatar\": null,\n  \"role\": \"admin_national\",\n  \"church\": 1\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Profile (PATCH)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"first_name\": \"Jean\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Martin\",\n  \"phone\": \"+22507080910\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/profile/",
            "description": "Met à jour prénom, nom, téléphone (email et rôle en lecture seule)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Change password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"old_password\": \"Motdepasse123!\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NouveauMotdepasse456!\",\n  \"new_password_confirm\": \"NouveauMotdepasse456!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/change-password/",
            "description": "**Réponse 200**\n```json\n{ \"detail\": \"Mot de passe modifié avec succès.\" }\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Users — Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/users/me/",
            "description": "Alias profil courant via ViewSet users."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
